{"tid":1292550,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"九龍反修例遊行 發起人稱有23萬人參與","createTime":"2019-07-07T11:17:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-07T13:34:18.000Z","uid":212626,"like":47,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"2c84c6161b454861962384f14b658c801c89533e","tid":1292550,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T11:17:37.000Z","msg":"有市民發起反對修訂《逃犯條例》大遊行，第一次在九龍舉行。遊行發起人劉穎匡表示，今日遊行人數有23萬。<br />\n<br />\n他又稱有遊行人士在彌敦道自由活動，故人數必然超過23萬人。<br />\n<br />\n遊行人士下午約三時半，提早半小時在尖沙咀梳士巴利花園起步，大批市民站滿附近一段彌敦道，隊頭下午四時許，抵達終點高鐵西九龍總站外空地。<br />\n<br />\n遊行人士沿凃高叫撤回修訂《逃犯條例》，及撤銷金鐘衝突的暴動定性等五大訴求。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2185440/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F2185440%2F&d=ycfrXf17TK8Hvu747cBakebr9%2BGymSeLOXabm6KdyvY%3D&h=e678eea3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2185440/</a>"},{"pid":"c494ea4d31aa04dce5487a41dbdcdacb9410e2c0","tid":1292550,"uid":108201,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T11:18:24.000Z","msg":"湯家樺，衰十一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02d21863641cd63d7d36a0f8c6132f84a58125d3","tid":1292550,"uid":212626,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T11:19:07.000Z","msg":"連續四次過十萬人幾大型遊行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2905d24a6a6b74fc8ed36fbf183588e37180d50","tid":1292550,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T11:19:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>連續四次過十萬人<span style=\"color: red;\">嘅</span>大型遊行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"1f2e4a0b0ceaafa01bc1a7db92ea029d21dbfe89","tid":1292550,"uid":173849,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2